description.en:
PYE is looking to fully disrupt the decentralized world! We have put together a team behind the PYE project to build PYECharts, PYESwap and PYEWallet which will revolutionize the future of cryptocurrency.  We are more than just a DeFi token, we are the future of Defi/Decentralization and CEXDEX. 

Join us on our way to the moon and be a part of making a true impact in the world! Together we can put a stop to world hunger and at the same time disrupt the decentralized world by offering better tech and more affordable access to everyone through mass adoption.
